eu.amidst.core.conceptdrift

Class MaximumLikelihoodFading

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.amidst.core.learning.parametric.ParallelMaximumLikelihood
      • eu.amidst.core.conceptdrift.MaximumLikelihoodFading
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FadingLearner, ParameterLearningAlgorithm

    public class MaximumLikelihoodFading
extends ParallelMaximumLikelihood
implements FadingLearner
    This class extends the ParallelMaximumLikelihood class and implements the FadingLearner interface. It defines the Maximum Likelihood Fading approach.

    For an example of use follow this link

    http://amidst.github.io/toolbox/CodeExamples.html#mlfadingexample
